      %p{:style => "font-size: 16px;"}
        With the support from the Global Fund, the Center for Malaria Parasitology and Entomology of Laos PDR (CMPE) uses Resource Map to report both the stock levels of life saving malaria drugs and the number of Malaria cases located at the village health centers up to the national level. Â This allows the Ministry of Health to have a real time visual picture of what resources are available and what is needed to treat patients.
    
    .clear
